---
import '../styles/globals.css';
import { siteConfig } from '../config.ts';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en-GB">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Privacy Policy | {siteConfig.site.name}</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Geist:wght@100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>
  <body class="text-brand-charcoal bg-[#f9f7f2] font-sans antialiased">
    <Navigation />
    
    <main class="pt-40 pb-24 px-4">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
        <h1 class="text-6xl font-black uppercase italic tracking-tighter mb-12">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        
        <div class="space-y-10 uppercase text-[11px] tracking-widest leading-relaxed opacity-90">
          <section class="border-l-2 border-brand-charcoal pl-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-black mb-4 italic">01. Data Controller</h2>
            <p>Lernit.io is a subsidiary of Jones Group. For the purposes of the Data Protection Act 2018 and the UK General Data Protection Regulation (UK GDPR), the data controller is Jones Group. We are committed to ensuring that your privacy is protected and that we are transparent about how we process your personal data.</p>
          </section>

          <section class="border-l-2 border-brand-charcoal pl-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-black mb-4 italic">02. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>We may collect and process the following data about you: Contact information (email address, telephone number), Identity data (name, username), Technical data (IP address, browser type, time zone setting), and Usage data (information about how you use our learning platforms).</p>
          </section>

          <section class="border-l-2 border-brand-charcoal pl-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-black mb-4 italic">03. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
            <p>We process your data only when we have a legal basis to do so. This includes: Performance of a contract (providing you with access to the platform), Legal obligation (tax and regulatory requirements), and Legitimate interests (improving our services and ensuring security).</p>
          </section>

          <section class="border-l-2 border-brand-charcoal pl-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-black mb-4 italic">04. Data Retention</h2>
            <p>We will only retain your personal data for as long as necessary to fulfil the purposes we collected it for, including for the purposes of satisfying any legal, accounting, or reporting requirements. Typically, this is for the duration of your active account plus six years for statutory limitation purposes.</p>
          </section>

          <section class="border-l-2 border-brand-charcoal pl-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-black mb-4 italic">05. Your Legal Rights</h2>
            <p>Under certain circumstances, you have rights under data protection laws in relation to your personal data, including the right to request access, correction, erasure, or restriction of processing. To exercise these rights, please contact us through the Jones Group portal.</p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>